*** gtmess version 0.9 (19 Dec 2004) ***

It's been more than one year since the previous version, and I've received
numerous emails about gtmess.  I've tried to incorporate all suggestions for
improvements. Thank you guys! Your feedback was precious.  Due to my
lack-of-free-time perhaps I forgot to answer some emails -- don't shoot me! :-)
This was also the reason it took me so long to release something new.  I have
slightly more free time now, that's why project has become alive again.

Enjoy the new version....

    	    	    	    	    	    	---- George
